              <div id="about-product-section">
               <div>
                <div>
                 <div>
                  <div class="product-about about-product-container">
                   <div class="Grid about-product-standard">
                    <div class="Grid-col u-size-9-12-m xs-padding-right about-product-description-container AboutThisItem">
                     <div>
                      <h2 class="about-product-title heading-b font-normal font-headline-4">
                       About This Item
                      </h2>
                     </div>
                     <div class="product-description-disclaimer xs-margin-top">
                      <span class="font-bold">
                       We aim to show you accurate product information.
                      </span>
                      <span>
                       Manufacturers,
            suppliers and others provide what you see here,
            and we have not verified it.
                       <button class="button prod-disclaimerButton button--link" data-automation-id="button" data-tl-id="button" type="button">
                        <span class="button-wrapper">
                         See our disclaimer
                        </span>
                       </button>
                      </span>
                     </div>
                     <span style="font-size:0">
                     </span>
                     <div class="about-desc about-product-description xs-margin-top">
                      <p>
                       <strong>
                        In-store activation offer available only at Walmart
                       </strong>
                      </p>
                      <p>
                       <strong>
                        iPhone 7 - $99 plus tax
                       </strong>
                      </p>
                      <ol>
                       <li>
                        iPhone 7 is carried in select Walmart stores. To check availability:
                        <ol style="list-style-type: lower-alpha;">
                         <li>
                          Look to the right under “Add to Cart” button and click on “More delivery &amp; pick up options.”
                         </li>
                         <li>
                          Select “Pickup” and enter your zip code.
                         </li>
                         <li>
                          You will see which stores in your area have the iPhone 7 in stock.
                         </li>
                        </ol>
                       </li>
                       <li>
                        Once at the store, head to the electronics counter.
                       </li>
                       <li>
                        A Walmart associate will help you:
                        <ol style="list-style-type: lower-alpha;">
                         <li>
                          Choose a plan of $50/month or higher
                         </li>
                         <li>
                          Activate your phone
                         </li>
                         <li>
                          Sign up for AutoPay
                         </li>
                        </ol>
                       </li>
                      </ol>
                      <p>
                       <strong>
                        Offer ends 10/17/20.
                       </strong>
                       Requires in-store activ. &amp; pymt. on new line of svc. on $50/mo. or higher plan, &amp; AutoPay signup. First mo. svc. charge &amp; applicable taxes due at sale. Excludes upgrades. Charges, fees usage &amp; other restr’s may apply. Details at
                       <a href="http://att.com/prepaidwalmart">
                        att.com/prepaidwalmart
                       </a>
                       .
                      </p>
                      <p>
                       iPhone 7 dramatically improves the most important aspects of the iPhone experience. It is water-resistant, so you're protected against spills, splashes, and even dust. The Home button on iPhone 7 is an advanced solid-state button designed to be durable, responsive, and pressure sensitive. Working in tandem with the Taptic Engine, it gives you precise tactile feedback as you press.
                      </p>
                      <p>
                       Using a highly advanced fingerprint sensor, Touch ID makes unlocking your iPhone 7 easy and secure. With Apple Pay, you can pay instantly and securely in stores, in apps, and on the web. And because your card details are never shared by Apple with merchants or stored on your device, using Apple Pay is the safer way to pay.
                      </p>
                      <p>
                       iPhone 7 comes with optical image stabilization to reduce blur associated with motion and handshake. A large aperture further enhances the camera's ability to take superb low-light photos. Teamed with the six-element lens, the camera will deliver brighter, more detailed shots. The flash adjusts according to the color temperature of the environment, resulting in sharper, more brightly lit photos.
                      </p>
                      <p>
                       The FaceTime HD camera is not only higher resolution, but it also uses wide color capture. So you can take sharper and more vibrant selfies. Worried about lighting? The Retina Flash matches the ambient light for a shot with natural-looking skin tones.
                      </p>
                      <p>
                       With a wide color gamut, the Retina HD display is able to deliver cinema-standard colors. More shades of the color spectrum can be used to create an image, meaning that what you see on the screen is a truer representation of the world.
                      </p>
                      <p>
                       With a four-core design, the A10 Fusion chip's CPU has two high-performance cores and two high-efficiency cores. The high-performance cores can run at up to 2x the speed of iPhone 6, while the high-efficiency cores are capable of running at just one-fifth the power of the high-performance cores. That means you get great performance and efficiency when you need it.
                      </p>
                     </div>
                     <span style="font-size:0">
                     </span>

NEW iphone earbuds are in a white case with a clear cover.  And the battery adapter/box had paper wrapping instead of plastic. The battery kept dying.  When I tried to charge it, it made a weird noise as if there was a short or something in the cord. But it didn't make that sound when I tried it on my old phone. Anyway, too many red flags for me to keep.  Bought me a phone from Best Buy.

                      <h2 class="PoliciesAndPlans-title">
                       Policies &amp; Plans
                      </h2>
                      <div class="vertical-tabber">
                       <div>
                        <div activetab="0" activetabclass="active" class="vertical-tabber-controls display-inline-block valign-top u-size-3-12" role="tablist">

                         <div class="active">
                          <div class="vertical-tabber-contents">
                           <div title="Warranty plan">
                            <h3 class="hide-content-m section-title">
                             Warranty plan
                            </h3>
                            <div class="arrange arrange-spaced">
                             <span style="font-size:0">
                             </span>
                             <div class="arrange-fill section-content">
                              <div class="font-bold u-textBlack">
                               Walmart Protection Plans
                              </div>
                              <div>
                               Most items come with a limited manufacturer’s warranty. The addition of a Walmart Protection Plan adds extra protection from the date of purchase. Walmart Protection Plans cover the total cost of repair, or replacement, for products, as well as covering delivery charges for the exchange.
                              </div>
                              <div class="m-margin-top">
                               <span>
                                Walmart Protection Plan options and pricing can be found on the product page, as well as in your cart. Go to
                               </span>
                               <a class="xxs-margin-left" href="//www.walmart.com/protection" target="_blank">
                                www.walmart.com/protection
                               </a>
                               <span class="xxs-margin-left">
                                to see all the coverage offered for each product. You can view your Walmart Protection Plan after your purchase in the Walmart Protection Plan Hub.
                               </span>
                              </div>
                              <div class="m-margin-top">
                               <span class="font-bold">
                                Product warranty:
                               </span>
                               <span class="xxs-margin-left">
                               </span>
                               <span class="display-block">
                                <button class="button button--link" data-automation-id="button" data-tl-id="button" type="button">
                                 <span class="button-wrapper">
                                  See details
                                  <i class="elc-icon xxs-margin-left elc-icon-down-arrow">
                                  </i>
                                 </span>
                                </button>
                                <div class="collapsable" style="min-height:0px">
                                 <div class="collapsable-content-container">
                                  <div class="m-margin-top">
                                   <span class="font-bold">
                                    Warranty Information:
                                   </span>
                                   <span class="xxs-margin-left">
                                    Apple One (1) Year Limited Warranty
                                   </span>
                                  </div>
                                  <div style="position:absolute;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;overflow:hidden;z-index:-1;visibility:hidden;pointer-events:none">
                                   <div style="position:absolute;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;overflow:hidden;z-index:-1;visibility:hidden;pointer-events:none">
                                    <div style="position:absolute;left:0;top:0;transition:0s;width:100000px;height:100000px">
                                    </div>
                                   </div>
                                   <div style="position:absolute;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;overflow:hidden;z-index:-1;visibility:hidden;pointer-events:none">
